                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18071028-74-off411 t18071028-74-cd412"></join>, three sacks, value 3 s two bushels and a half of potatoes, value 5 s. and five bushels of chaff, value 2 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
